1. `Active` **Volcanoes**: These volcanoes remain open and erupt frequently.*Examples:* [Mount Etna](https://www.go-etna.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/mount_etna-600x450.jpg) (Italy), [Cotopaxi](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/74/V%C3%B3lcan_Cotopaxi.jpg/330px-V%C3%B3lcan_Cotopaxi.jpg) (Ecuador)

