3. `Extinct` **Volcanoes**: These volcanoes have not erupted in known geological periods. Their vents remain closed, often forming crater lakes.*Example:* [Popa](https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/09/d4/1a/e9/mount-popa.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=-1&amp;s=1) (Myanmar)
